Package: revolver
Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2026-06-29
Title: REVOLVER: Repeated Evolution in Cancer
Type: Package
Maintainer: Giulio Caravagna <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Giulio", "Caravagna", email = "gcaravagn@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ylenia", "Giarratano", email = "ylenia.giarratano@gmail.com", role = "ctb"),
    person("Daniele", "Ramazzotti", email = "daniele.ramazzotti@yahoo.com", role = "ctb"),
    person("Luca", "De Sano", email = "luca.desano@gmail.com", role = "ctb"))
Description: Implements the statistical framework described in Caravagna et al.
    (2018) <doi:10.1038/s41592-018-0108-x> for inferring repeated evolutionary
    trajectories of cancer from multi-region tumour sequencing data. Given a
    cohort of patients with phylogenetic trees, the package fits a probabilistic
    model of repeated evolution, clusters patients by shared trajectories, and
    provides tools for visualisation and jackknife-based stability assessment.

